      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MISS BLUE STORK (3) has been terrific since joining Josh Farrugia, recording four wins and a city second from five outings. Came from the back row to salute by 7.5 metres at Penrith last start. Won easily the only time she attempted this circuit and distance and the good draw should see her hard to stop. SIR KNIGHT (1) drew very wide and wasn't too far away last start at Menangle. Came from this barrier for a Penrith win the last time he raced outside of the city so is better placed. PENURIOUS (2) draws lower than in his last-start fourth and recorded a string of top-three finishes prior including a win here. Respect. ROCKNROLL CLARRY (5) must be included off a win from this barrier two back at Menangle.",
